---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Wassim Serhan Photographs">
	<main class="about">
		<div class="content">
			<h1>About</h1>
			<p class="bio">
				Wassim Serhan is a photographer who lives and works in New York City. From a young age, Wassim has always had an interest in people, a curiosity that inspired him to create photographs, turning the mundane into a spectacle illusion. Wassim’s passion for candid street style photography started in 2003 where he was part of the team filming a documentary about Haiti. Intuition is a key factor in Wassim’s street photography work; using the streets as scenes to communicate and story-tell. Travel is important for Wassim, learning about new cultures, and using the streets as visual playground for inspiration for new bodies of work.
			</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="cta">Get in touch</a>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about {
		padding-top: 64px;
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.content {
		max-width: 560px;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	h1 {
		font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: 0.3em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #f0f0f0;
		margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
	}

	.bio {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.85;
		color: #999;
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.available {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #666;
		margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.cta {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		font-size: 0.68rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: 0.22em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #888;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		padding-bottom: 2px;
		transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
	}

	.cta:hover {
		color: #f0f0f0;
		border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
	}
</style>
